                'title' => '页面功能及介绍',
                'content' => '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;一、&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;APP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;页面及功能介绍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px;text-indent: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;分为四个部分，“特卖”、“找尖货”、“奶牙圈”、“购物车”及“我的”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px;text-indent: 0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;“特卖”页面&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px;text-indent: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;75.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618182935510.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618182935510.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;a．&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;商品分类页面&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;通过“热门分类”、“手动搜索”及“商品分类”查看或选择商品，如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;76.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618197109378.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618197109378.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;b．&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;签到&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px;text-indent: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;签到规则如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;77.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618214923634.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618214923634.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;签到页面如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;78.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618230116865.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618230116865.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11.818181991577148px&quot;&gt;连续签到10天，系统自动兑换一张10元代金券，连续签到满一个自然月，将获得20元代金券的全勤奖，全勤奖会当时返到账户中。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;c．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif&quot;&gt;抱团&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;80.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618271194245.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618271194245.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;d．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height: 24px&quot;&gt;拍下宝宝照片，自定义标上卖萌价，分享给朋友卖萌讨钱咯。如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;81.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618286770441.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618286770441.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 24px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;f．&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;掌上秒杀&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;秒杀，有价格优势，但有数量限制，如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;83.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618322893511.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618322893511.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;“奶牙圈”首页&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12.380952835083008px&quot;&gt;奶牙圈关注、点赞、评论及分享操作如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;84.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618341561564.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618341561564.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;line-height: 173%;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;购物车&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;奶牙购物车中会显示下单规则，也可进行增加或删减商品数量及进行商品删除的操作，如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;85.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618367109094.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618367109094.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &amp;#39;微软雅黑&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;sans-serif&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;结算页面如下图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;86.jpg&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/20160704/1467618390525848.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1467618390525848.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
                'ctime' => 1467618406,
